{"tid":1625971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"某校長：因為有咁多無知嘅學生香港真係好可憐","createTime":"2019-10-05T09:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T07:55:24.000Z","uid":133582,"like":118,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"fe322ecdcc0c8fc7923c2ddfde618386daefaa7d","tid":1625971,"uid":133582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"（借acc代post）<br />\n<br />\n李求恩紀念中學校長（賴炳華）<br />\n非常紅底，開學到而家不斷打壓學生<br />\n<br />\n本年度有兩個學生會候選內閣，其中一個內閣有兩位為學校關注組成員，校長早前於早會介紹，對另一個候選內閣係咁讚，但到了<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">有關注組成員嘅候選內閣</span></strong>時，當住<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">全校面挑剔和針對</span></strong>。到班房宣傳的時候都一直針鋒相對，問有關注組成員的候選內閣時，問佢地話會幫學生做佢哋想做嘅嘢，咁係咪即係代表學生唔想返學，唔想着校服，係咪都會幫佢哋做。<br />\n<br />\n加上某日早會，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">校長於全校前講示威者不是</span></strong>，雖然冇講立場，但在整個分享當中，只係<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">不斷講示威者不是，完全沒有多角度為學生分析，只講示威者破壞</span></strong>，同埋話<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">嗌口號嘅時候目無表情，其做法不過係人云亦云和羊群心理</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">指責示威者根本不知自己為什麼要示威，還批評消防員</span></strong>，為何沒有阻止示威者和評論示威者毫不緊張認真，從容不迫地換衫然後傾去邊度食嘢。<br />\n<br />\n到了當天第一個小息，大部份<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">高中同學到操場，唱願榮光歸香港以及嗌口號</span></strong>（光復香港時代革命，香港人加油）老師沒有阻止只從旁觀望，然後<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">校長見到我地嘅行為，馬上黑面</span></strong>。高中同學在第一個小息鐘便返回課室，但在第二個小息鐘響時，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">馬上叫全部高中同學到禮堂舉行特別周會</span></strong>，內容重點如下<br />\n1.叫我地要互相尊重唔同意見嘅同學 （想講佢早會講啲嘢都好唔尊重我哋另外一邊嘅立場）<br />\n2.我哋咁樣做會傷左其他同學嘅心（校長你都好傷我哋心）<br />\n3.唔好係學校講政治，唔好將政治帶入校園裏面，分化同學 （朝頭早講嘅嘢咪已經帶入左囉）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">佢叫發聲嘅同學要顧及其他同學<br />\n即係叫我地收聲。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n然而我哋學校係有升旗<br />\n老師同我地講話要尊重場合<br />\n喺<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">校長分享嘅時間，佢話佢係中國人，但係整個分享入面佢完全冇用過廣東話或者普通話分享<br />\n一直用英文講嘢，唔通你又有尊重場合？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外 係10月4號（教師發展日唔需要返學）同學A 11點時俾校長勒令半個小時內回校 <br />\n但返到學校後比校務處嘅職員通知同學A校長要去食飯同埋開會 <br />\n該<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">同學等左7小時先見到校長 </span></strong>喺等候校長嘅期間不斷接見老師同埋社工加上要寫個案紙<br />\n（老師講既內容包括<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong>要同學A應承老師以後唔好再參與社會運動</strong></strong></span> 並同學生問值唔值得為咗場運動而冇咗個阿媽）直至見校長 ，一開始校長要該同學望住阿媽 但因為同學佢心情唔好所以冇望到<br />\n但校長竟然挑釁該同學話你係咪心虛啊點解唔肯望你呀嗎？<br />\n然後校長不斷問同學A反送中字眼嘅問題 例如義士嘅定義係咩 雙普選係咩 <br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有D侮辱性嘅說話e.g.香港好可憐 因為有咁多好似同學A呢D無知嘅學生<br />\n仲叫同學讀多啲書</span></strong></strong><br />\n到最後就話唔想再同佢講野 就叫番佢出去<br />\n校長仲同佢屋企人講 <strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以安全為理由要禁足同學A 直至星期二</span></strong></strong>（8號）<br />\n仲要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">介紹內地嘅學校比該同學嘅媽咪</span></strong> 並講同學身在福中不知 仲話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><strong><strong>夠膽就唔好飲東江水 做得到就係英雄做唔到就係狗熊</strong></strong></strong></strong> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據聞之前校長有同其他同學講 唔好睇咁多報紙 見識少就要睇多啲書"},{"pid":"8c92877d3209dd2cbb08b117fcd30604de0e47cc","tid":1625971,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"E"},{"pid":"40e99aafb390f16ab2b16a3b036cef1b4dc3c47d","tid":1625971,"uid":144784,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母上海仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b30776ef719646d6ee69a3fdf443c72f220b4e6","tid":1625971,"uid":279253,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"「唔好睇咁多報紙 見識少就要睇多啲書」呢句真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce9481eba3e0b464cac0367326edcf31491468b","tid":1625971,"uid":83145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:18:39.000Z","msg":"推爆佢 仆街校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194c8b58277a1806490e4ed8c347007ba1e68aa0","tid":1625971,"uid":286173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:19:17.000Z","msg":"為人師表喎🤷🏽&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"248e4ec0b1196ea835b4f6dad9e3427a87ab6653","tid":1625971,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"8a54220b76075ddadee65cc256c4f55d0e0f4c2b","tid":1625971,"uid":270999,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"我都係李求恩嘅學生，賴炳華話示威者唔比消防車入，但明明2百萬人都可以分條紅海比巴士行，分明抹黑手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲校長點解唔去食屎</span></span>"},{"pid":"91b77d398b3073e96fbfd66824ff07d895077373","tid":1625971,"uid":245499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"校友識做啦<br />\n唔好比佢係咁打壓師弟師妹"},{"pid":"ba9db10804f691db87eabee831df86798650a7ba","tid":1625971,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"校友幫推"},{"pid":"cb756bf6b0941812169289302d08721df1faccb1","tid":1625971,"uid":303133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"藍字好難睇.. 推"},{"pid":"d6051c7c24c39f2f2b249a0a5f1fc9931da0f621","tid":1625971,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"其實學生黑警都唔驚洗撚驚學校咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反9佢啦"},{"pid":"259f998f3840666792bc02ef826bad6a89adcce7","tid":1625971,"uid":39137,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:24:12.000Z","msg":"唔意外<br />\n呢位校長已經多次因為唔同事件見報<br />\n迫害老師 威嚇學生<br />\n校董會都仲繼續用佢證明係辦學團體本身都有問題"},{"pid":"972447800081f3bc35a014255574c153c531491b","tid":1625971,"uid":87640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:24:31.000Z","msg":"幫推 咁冇文化都做到校長"},{"pid":"c77439232bed4b38f467805a4cc0c89952569e3c","tid":1625971,"uid":196254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"107d1cff0effc87ee4e1bf58165f7a0b90824cde","tid":1625971,"uid":237656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:25:19.000Z","msg":"同我推上熱門 幫佢個校長室維修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e511b0fbb06a1bb63365d2d66dfb1bae1a6d0103","tid":1625971,"uid":317842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190111/mobile/bkn-20190111135545388-0111_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190111%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190111135545388-0111_00822_001.html&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=077ba8db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190111/mobile/bkn-20190111135545388-0111_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n係咪公報私仇呢？！"},{"pid":"2a3ac8be5000dc78f573fb3e53d9ef4c67c12019","tid":1625971,"uid":270999,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:27:57.000Z","msg":"呢個校長一直而來都做啲on9野 又打老師 又無故解僱體育老師"},{"pid":"be18d676b9c43aef07072477b426299afc46599f","tid":1625971,"uid":31545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"D廢老真係好鍾意講東江水  呢D垃圾論點最好駁返佢啦  次次都講"},{"pid":"eaeb52cad98ef8d433a7b3b33931e5543ec9a6af","tid":1625971,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ddc58bcb50a51c21b3fd904e397453739982192","tid":1625971,"uid":8589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢條仆街幾時死 <br />\n玩大啲 師弟師妹我支持你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be37cbba35a8dac88eb1ecac5036b6d0a67988c","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"都估到佢冇咁好死，我問啲師弟妹校長有冇恰佢地，雖然佢地話冇，但我唔太信，當年我讀嗰陣呢個所謂校長已經好似林鄭咁不斷打壓佢唔鍾意既老師，整係識刷校董鞋（其中一位校董係佢中學時期既英文老師），仲有睇唔起成績差既同學，迫到老師抑鬱壓力爆煲，背後做好多手段令校董都唔鍾意唔順佢意既老師，好多畢左業既同學都知<br />\n<br />\n仲有前幾年佢為左迫左一直受學生愛戴既訓導老師將莫須有罪名加係人地身上，仲要開學前幾日先同人地講，但佢已經一早請左人頂果個訓導老師個位，根本係想令個老師搵唔切工，件事上曬新聞<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢曾經因爲襲擊助教定唔記得老師而上新聞<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得點解佢咁多年都冇事？因為佢背後有一班同共產黨咁既人撐住佢，間學校同中共一模一樣！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7e1b0145ab32090070255b7aca8dc3fd91d72a72","tid":1625971,"uid":265313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:37:40.000Z","msg":"推到畀記者知"},{"pid":"1feb0d3ebefcabfa1af707e307cac3c003f947b7","tid":1625971,"uid":236011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:39:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母上海仔<br />\n呢條仆街幾撚時死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲讀緊個陣已經覺得佢假仁假義 成日扮撚曬幫啲學生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffd1e260ae35a687d5b7f768e2b785d62e82609","tid":1625971,"uid":270999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fed7aefc1ff77a78d019ba6307051fd4a6de46b7","tid":1625971,"uid":242815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"一直話要尊重其他人 反而自己就都唔尊重其他人<br />\n垃圾校長"},{"pid":"036bbf6c601efc0442438bb4dca432c09d4820de","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"2325c1ba71b48953f40fbe60c25d547cf5483b95","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cedbafe9e70631ae47530fc50db78d2c2e19d49","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"仲有佢住學校6樓，佢自稱因爲佢住新界校董體諒佢住得遠，所以俾佢住係嗰度，當時好多老師比佢住得更遠憑咩佢可以住學校？<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣聽人講6樓年年暑假都裝修"},{"pid":"bbd7d7709cadd2eba848c1b89fb74aff9c542c2d","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾校長幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600f4417077c4002a8c5b7d96af200726f929e4","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"一啲都唔似為人師表<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce0abebbdfcfbb7450da0f90f8c36517d43cfc4","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d30df780c53220fdc2b9ace4142ffa3ea65e95","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4dd5ba1fce0692627da8642745e2982b50060f","tid":1625971,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20